<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>点餐系统简化版</title>
    <style>
        .cook {
            width: 400px;
            height: 400px;
            background-color: #ccc;
            margin: 50px auto;
            padding: 100px;
        }

        input {
            outline: none;
            height: 25px;
            width: 180px;
        }

        .cook h1 {
            text-align: center;
            color: #333;
        }

        .cook p {
            width: 100%;
            color: #333;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin: 50px 0;
        }

        .cook p:nth-child(4) {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .cook p:nth-child(4) #btn {
            width: 100px;
            height: 50px;
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 20px;
            background-color: #333;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="cook">
        <h1>点餐系统</h1>
        <p>
            请输入你的会员名/手机号：
            <input type="text" name="phone">
        </p>
        <p>请您输入你想要点的菜名：
            <input type="text" name="cooker">
        </p>
        <p>
            <input type="submit" value="确定" id="btn">
        </p>
        <a href="/allorder">查看所有的订单信息</a>
    </div>

</body>
<script src="/jquery1.11.3.js"></script>
</html>
